{"tid":1085923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人唔好輸呀！！","createTime":"2019-03-31T13:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T14:06:42.000Z","uid":149026,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b634a89cd8c3575d53fc4a4baece02323593e3a1","tid":1085923,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"雖然每日都話返工不了，但係今日真係見到有好多人遊行示威，其實好多人都仍然心繫香港. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cOWteqO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcOWteqO.png&h=64d108bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人唔好輸呀！！<br />\n<br />\n同熱愛這片土地，大家刻骨銘記. <br />\n冇抗爭，香港就只會被蠶食. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日冒雨前行， 我哋以後都要冒著風險去守護我地嘅香港. <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FwKZk5W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFwKZk5W.png&h=9f7d6cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係香港人，無論通過咩渠道都好，希望大家大家都為香港出一分力！"},{"pid":"20474464397f2c26a8345264259db32258cd739e","tid":1085923,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"算9數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b9dc9b1b8e96a81db7a58e631b54dc11f81161","tid":1085923,"uid":85774,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:59:52.000Z","msg":"唉 遊行有咩用"},{"pid":"db852357f8e721a1c5e3f30836baf560735a6ad2","tid":1085923,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20474464397f2c26a8345264259db32258cd739e","tid":1085923,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"算9數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"點解要咁灰？"},{"pid":"f9c3b8548fc96d9b83eb201db4427886d1be1601","tid":1085923,"uid":149026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17b9dc9b1b8e96a81db7a58e631b54dc11f81161","tid":1085923,"uid":85774,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-